text: Florida's 27th congressional district is a congressional district in the U.S. state of Florida. Republican Maria Elvira Salazar is the representative since elected in 2021. It contains all of Florida, including the cities of Miami, Miami Beach, Coral Gables, and Kendall. The neighborhood of Little Havana is in this district. == References == Category:Government of Florida Category:Congressional districts of Florida
title: Florida's 27th congressional district
